para ipaghiganti ang namatay mong magulang?

00:06:16.550 --> 00:06:17.780
At paano si Baek Sul Hee?

00:06:18.350 --> 00:06:20.690
Mula nang malaman niyang si Mi So ay
kanyang sariling laman at dugo,

00:06:21.220 --> 00:06:23.120
